name: Adorabilis Octopus
description:
Adorabilis Octopus is Cosmic Blaze's best friend.

They meet during one of his space expeditions on the Blue planet.

Adorabilis lived in the sea. He now swims in space without any difficulty.

It’s abnormalty is that it does not grow up or become old. Some people say he is immortal.

Health: +20 
Armor: + 15
